	Je suis <span class = "name">Martin Bodin</span><sup><a href = "#familyName_fr">1</a></sup>, post-doctorant au <a href = "https://www.imperial.ac.uk/"><span class = "name">Imperial College</span></a>, à <span class = "town">Londres</span>, dans le groupe de recherche <a href = "https://vtss.doc.ic.ac.uk/">Verified Trustworthy Software Specification</a>.
